VALUES.VALUE: NABARUN is a fully charitable and non profit organization, here everything is depend upon the members. So, if anyone wants to help us by any suggestion, any idea or any planning related to our group or upcoming work or about our social media handles then he/she can write those to nabarunbangla18@gmail.com.

Their must be a group meeting in every month end and several important meetings can occur before any field work. So, if anyone misses that meeting, it's his/her responsibility to get updated with all those necessary information.

Those members are only added by the group coordinators (after sharing wp number by the person wants to add them) and they are welcomed by only the person wants to add him/her and by the group coordinator.

Several persons are assigned for the duties in the group, but they are not given any benefits for doing those. The only thing for which they are managing their time from everything is the love and dedication towards this group. So, every member must respect them and in their field their decisions are always the final.
Proper courtesy and good as well as friendly behavior is expected from every members in the group. Remember your behavior should not hurt others.
Unnecessary talks, unrelated posts must be avoided in the group, only group work related conversations are appreciated.
Group members should clear their donation within 15th of every month and their payments are approved after giving screenshots in the group.
If any member is having any problem or query related to group then he/she must consult with the group coordinators within the group. He/she will not bother other members by personal text.
